@startuml
title ATM Control - Greet User and Check PIN

[*] --> Idle

state Idle
state "Waiting for Card Insertion" as WaitingForCardInsertion
state "Waiting for PIN" as WaitingForPIN
state "Validating PIN" as ValidatingPIN
state Greeting
state Confiscating
state Ejecting

Idle --> Greeting : Arrival / Display Welcome
Greeting --> WaitingForCardInsertion : Card Inserted / Get PIN

WaitingForCardInsertion --> ValidatingPIN : PIN Entered / Validate PIN
ValidatingPIN --> WaitingForPIN : Invalid PIN / Invalid PIN Prompt

ValidatingPIN --> Confiscating : Third Invalid PIN,\nCard Stolen, Card Expired /\nConfiscate
ValidatingPIN --> Ejecting : Cancel / Eject
WaitingForCardInsertion --> Ejecting : Cancel / Eject

@enduml
